{"tid":1354303,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"致各位飽受屋企政見不合困擾既各位","createTime":"2019-07-23T06:15:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T06:34:55.000Z","uid":282006,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"37ece8527deafab1e22659c949ba3b059b52c6c8","tid":1354303,"uid":282006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:15:18.000Z","msg":"廢時post時事台阻住大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小弟做左cd-rom一段日子，因為呢一段日子既事而開個ac，亦因為有d野想同大家講，我無決心做勇武，但同時我想幫下其他受困擾既人抒緩下，因為少一樣記掛，就多一份精神去撐香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我相信到而家呢一刻仲有唔少&ldquo;人&rdquo;撐警，撐黑，撐政府而帶比各位巴絲無比既壓力<br />\n可能你出於各種原因而啞忍，或者同佢地衝突，更甚者好似啱啱離去既手足咁，永遠無機會睇到呢個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實小弟之見，屋企有呢種&ldquo;人&rdquo;（我信人選擇相信d咩同性格有關，而亦係最難以改變）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不論呢個幾月既事有無發生，到最後只要一有事屋企個和諧表象就會馬上破裂，不見得以後唔會家嘈屋閉，而帶比自己更大壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而我亦都知以香港咁既環境，其實好難話永遠逃離<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過其實諗深一層<br />\n大家先更要趁有呢個幾月發生既事，搵番大家既同路人，有更多既機會可以互相幫助，無謂同所謂屋企人糾纏<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家一齊撐住<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我相信呢個幾月既事帶比我地既唔止困擾，其實仲係機會，可以拉番近香港人本來就疏離左既距離<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">大家撐住，唔想再失去任何一位</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cf22b7fe9d0bb65a4ead5f76020ed439f18a365","tid":1354303,"uid":265824,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:31:49.000Z","msg":"唔好話屋企人係藍絲,好朋友係藍,或扮晒唔表態,卻暗地屌示威者攪亂香港我都感覺好難受<br />\n唔好氣餒,我地係同路人,1條心,香港人加油 !<br />\n(廢中絲打)"},{"pid":"3542a27d3e25f8441df694e93ebd6cbd46ef0915","tid":1354303,"uid":282006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:32:19.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c615a55adc82fc0615b29b11a0cf1da7864c07e","tid":1354303,"uid":282006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:32:56.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd1dc2e721252c33539d0d4aa02408383954c48f","tid":1354303,"uid":282006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:34:55.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}